result.title: Help me to find a University.
result.content:
At the moment I am in high school in Moldova, this year I graduate. I am struggling to find a good and cheap university. I want to study abroad, somewhere where knowledge is much more valuable than what you have in your pocket and competitiveness should be present too. If you have time could you tell me your way of getting admit, how much you pay or paid?
P.S. I know about MIT, Caltech ..., but I am not a dreamer.
